(368697, 11502, 367039, 'jog3ee', 4022, '', 1370245686, 'Oh by the way we also had an hw80 belonging to Turumti but that couldn''t be worked upon and was only tested on chrony, which averaged 615 fps with Crosman pellets, which wasn''t bad for a gun that''s at least 12-13 years old :) And of course there was the slingshot which helped feeding a cat ;)', 1, 0, '202.61.45.12', 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 'on_nl2br', 0, 0),
